Class ScriptableList

  • java.lang.Object
    • sun.org.mozilla.javascript.NativeJavaObject
      • com.randomnoun.common.jessop.engine.rhinoOpenjdk.ScriptableList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, sun.org.mozilla.javascript.Scriptable, sun.org.mozilla.javascript.Wrapper

    public class ScriptableList
extends sun.org.mozilla.javascript.NativeJavaObject
    ScriptableList is a wrapper for java.util.List instances that allows developers to interact with them like it was a native JavaScript array.
